ActBank Act
Trust and Loan Companies Act
Cooperative Credit Associations Act
SubjectPrescribed Products Regulations
PrecisPRESCRIBED PRODUCTS REGULATIONS, in order to define "prescribed products" for the purposes of the financial institution statutes. Prescribed products are considered to be either deposit type instruments, as defined in the Deposit Type Instruments Regulations, or principal protected notes, as defined in the Principal Protected Notes Regulations.
